{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "POP/awaken", "tags": "grains"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Awaken By Geometry"], "extent": [33, 56]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Activates particles near animated geometry."], "extent": [56, 108]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [108, 123], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is used as a way to optimize your sand simulations. It will only activate particles near animated geometry, so that only a small part of your simulation is actually running at any give time. You would typically use this tool whenever you're running a sand simulation where only a small portion of the sand will be directly affected by your animation object. For example, if you have a character walking across the desert. "], "extent": [123, 558]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The initial setup occurs in SOPs where the animated object is converted to a volume and then expanded. The expanded volume is used to activate the sand nearby the animated object. In DOPs, a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/popawaken", "type": "link", "text": ["POP Awaken"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popawaken"}, " node will be added, with the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Awaken by Volume"]}, " checkbox turned on."], "extent": [558, 852]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [852, 858], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Make sure you either turn on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Enable Auto Sleep"]}, " checkbox on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Sleeping"]}, " tab of the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/popsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["POP Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popsolver"}, " or use the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/autosleep", "type": "link", "text": ["Auto-Sleep Particles"], "fullpath": "/shelf/autosleep"}, " tool on the Grains shelf first."], "extent": [858, 1073]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Awaken By Geometry"], "extent": [1073, 1104], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select the object that will awaken the particles."], "extent": [1104, 1158]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "POP/awaken", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/POP/awaken"}, {"type": "ui", "text": ["Awaken By Geometry"]}, " tool on the Grains tab. "], "extent": [1158, 1236]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For specific parameter information, see the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbreshapesdf", "type": "link", "text": ["VDB Reshape SDF"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbreshapesdf"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/popawaken", "type": "link", "text": ["POP Awaken"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popawaken"}, " help pages."], "extent": [1236, 1374]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [1374, 1379], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Offset"]}, " parameter on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbreshapesdf", "type": "link", "text": ["VDB Reshape SDF"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbreshapesdf"}, " SOP controls how far away from the animated object the sand will be activated."], "extent": [1379, 1536]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The green areas show particles that are awake, and the red areas show particles that are sleeping."], "extent": [1536, 1636]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/wake_sleep1.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}, "\n", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/wake_sleep3.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1636, 1716]}]}], "title": ["Awaken By Geometry"], "summary": ["Activates particles near animated geometry."]}